\c 21
\s Umnikelo womfelokazi
\p
\v 1 Wathi ephakamisa amehlo wabona abanothileyo\x + Mark. 12.41-44.\x* bephosela iminikelo yabo esitsheni somnikelo\x + 21.1,5.\x*.
\v 2 Wabona lomfelokazi othile ongumyanga ephosela khona inhlamvana ezincane ezimbili zemali.
\v 3 Wathi: Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Lumfelokazi ongumyanga uphosele okwedlula okwabo bonke;
\v 4 ngoba bonke laba baphosele kokunengi kwabo eminikelweni kaNkulunkulu\x + 21.1,5.\x*, kodwa yena ebuyangeni bakhe uphosele konke alakho abephila \add ngakho\add*.
\s UJesu ukhuluma ngokuchithwa kweJerusalema langokuphela kwesikhathi
\p
\v 5 Abanye besakhuluma ngethempeli, ukuthi liceciswe ngamatshe amahle\x + Mat. 24.1-51. Mark. 13.1-37.\x* langezipho, wathi:
\v 6 Lezizinto elizibonayo, kuzafika insuku okungayikutshiywa ngazo ilitshe phezu kwelitshe, elingayikudilizelwa phansi\x + 19.44.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Basebembuza, besithi: Mfundisi, pho lezizinto zizakuba nini? Lesibonakaliso siyini, lapho sekuzakwenzeka lezizinto?
\v 8 Wasesithi: Qaphelani ukuthi lingaduhiswa; ngoba abanengi bazakuza ebizweni lami\x + 17.23.\x*, besithi: Ngi\add nguye\x + Mat. 24.5.\x*\add*; futhi: Isikhathi sesisondele. Ngakho lingabalandeli\x + 17.23.\x*.
\v 9 Njalo nxa lisizwa ngezimpi langeziphithiphithi\x + 1 Kor. 14.33.\x*, lingethuki\x + 24.37.\x*; ngoba lezizinto zimele ukuthi zenzeke kuqala, kodwa ukuphela kakuhle ku\add fik\add*e\x + 17.7. Mat. 13.21.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Wasesithi kubo: Isizwe sizavukela isizwe, lombuso u\add vuk\add*ele umbuso;
\v 11 njalo kuzakuba khona ukuzamazama komhlaba okukhulu indawo ngendawo lezindlala labomatshayabhuqe bezifo; kube khona lezinto ezesabekayo lezibonakaliso ezinkulu ezivela ezulwini.
\p
\v 12 Kodwa ngaphambi kwakho konke lokhu bazalibamba ngezandla zabo, ba\add li\add*zingele\x + Mat. 10.17-22.\x*, ba\add li\add*nikele emasinagogeni lezintolongweni, ba\add li\add*se phambi kwamakhosi lababusi, ngenxa yebizo lami\x + Seb. 4.3. 5.18. 12.4. 16.24. 21.27. 2 Kor. 11.23. Mat. 10.18.\x*.
\v 13 Njalo \add lokhu\add* kuzaphenduka kini kube yibufakazi\x + Fil. 1.28. 2 Thes. 1.5.\x*.
\v 14 Ngakho kubekeni enhliziyweni zenu\x + 9.44. 1.66.\x* ukuthi linganakani ngaphambili \add nge\add*lizakuphendula\x + 12.11.\x*;
\v 15 ngoba mina ngizalinika umlomo lenhlakanipho, abangekuphike, bamelane lakho\x + Eks. 4.12.\x*, bonke abayizitha zenu.
\v 16 Njalo lizanikelwa langabazali labafowenu lezihlobo labangane, njalo bazabulala \add abanye\add* benu.
\v 17 Njalo lizazondwa yibo bonke ngenxa yebizo lami.
\v 18 Kodwa kakuyikulahleka ngitsho unwele lwekhanda lenu\x + Mat. 10.30. 1 Sam. 14.45.\x*.
\v 19 Ekubekezeleni kwenu\x + Roma 5.3. Jak. 1.3.\x* zuzani imiphefumulo yenu\x + Mat. 10.9. Seb. 1.18. 8.20. 22.28. Luka 18.12. 1 Thes. 4.4.\x*.
\p
\v 20 Kodwa nxa libona iJerusalema ihanqwe ngamabutho\x + 19.43.\x*, yazini-ke ukuthi sekusondele ukuchitheka kwayo\x + Dan. 9.27.\x*.
\v 21 Ngalesosikhathi abaseJudiya kababalekele ezintabeni; labaphakathi kwayo baphume; labasemaphandleni\x + Joha. 4.35. Jak. 5.4.\x* bangangeni kuyo\x + 17.31.\x*.
\v 22 Ngoba lezi zinsuku zempindiselo\x + 18.7,8. Mat. 24.22.\x*, ukuze kugcwaliseke zonke izinto ezilotshiweyo\x + Dan. 9.24-27. 12.1.\x*.
\v 23 Kodwa maye kwabakhulelweyo labamunyisayo ngalezonsuku! Ngoba kuzakuba khona ukuhlupheka okukhulu emhlabeni, lolaka kulesisizwe\x + 1 Kor. 7.26.\x*.
\v 24 Njalo bazakuwa ngobukhali benkemba, bathunjelwe ezizweni zonke\x + Heb. 11.34. Gen. 34.26.\x*; leJerusalema inyathelelwe phansi ngabezizwe\x + Isam. 11.2. Dan. 8.13.\x*, kuze kugcwaliseke izikhathi zabezizwe\x + Dan. 12.7. Roma 11.25.\x*.
\p
\v 25 Kuzakuba khona izibonakaliso elangeni lenyangeni lezinkanyezini; lemhlabeni usizi lwezizwe ngokudideka\x + 2 Kor. 2.4.\x*; kudume ulwandle lamagagasi,
\v 26 abantu baphele amandla ngenxa yokwesaba langokulindela lokho okuzayo emhlabeni; ngoba amandla amazulu azazanyazanyiswa\x + Mat. 24.14.\x*.
\v 27 Khona-ke bezayibona iNdodana yomuntu isiza eyezini ilamandla lenkazimulo enkulu.
\v 28 Njalo nxa kuqala ukwenzeka lezizinto, manini liqonde njalo liphakamise amakhanda enu\x + 13.11.\x*; ngoba kusondele ukukhululwa kwenu\x + Roma 8.23. Efe. 4.30.\x*.
\p
\v 29 Wasebatshela umfanekiso: Khangelani umkhiwa lazo zonke izihlahla;
\v 30 nxa sezihluma, liyazibonela lani likwazi ukuthi ihlobo selisondele.
\v 31 Ngokunjalo lani, nxa libona lezizinto zisenzeka, yazini ukuthi umbuso kaNkulunkulu useduze.
\v 32 Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Lesisizukulwana asisoze sidlule, kuze kwenzeke zonke izinto.
\v 33 Kuzadlula izulu lomhlaba, kodwa amazwi ami kawasoze adlule\x + 12.57.\x*.
\p
\v 34 Njalo ziqapheleni\x + 17.3.\x*, ukuthi inhliziyo zenu zingasindwa ngenxa yokuminza lokudakwa\x + Roma 13.13. 1 Pet. 4.7.\x* lokuphisekela izinto zalokhukusila\x + 1 Kor. 6.3,4.\x*, lalolosuku lulifikele lingananzelele\x + 1 Thes. 5.3. Luka 12.40.\x*;
\v 35 ngoba luzafika njengomjibila phezu kwabo bonke abahlezi ebusweni bomhlaba wonke\x + Tshu. 9.12.\x*.
\v 36 Ngakho lindani ngezikhathi zonke\x + Mark. 13.33.\x* likhulekele\x + 18.1.\x* ukuthi lifanele ukuphepha zonke lezizinto ezizakwenzeka\x + 20.35.\x*, lokuma phambi kweNdodana yomuntu\x + Isam. 6.17. Efe. 6.13,14. Hlab. 1.5.\x*.
\p
\v 37 Njalo wayefundisa\x + Mat. 26.55.\x* ethempelini emini\x + Joha. 8.2.\x*; kodwa ebusuku wayephuma ayehlala\x + Mat. 21.17. Luka 22.39. Joha. 18.2.\x* entabeni ethiwa ngeyeMihlwathi\x + Joha. 8.1.\x*.
\v 38 Lekuseni kakhulu abantu bonke babesiza kuye\x + Joha. 8.2.\x* ethempelini ukumuzwa\x + Joha. 8.2.\x*.